article_title: Voice of the People: Talking Obamacare in Times Square
article_text:
Published on Sep 18, 2013

Heritage's Chris Jacobs visited New York City to ask people about Obamacare. Do you think it's hazardous to your health? Let us know in the comments. | http://obamacare.heritage.org/
